Class DecoratedJsonObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.ingsw.util.json.DecoratedJsonObject
  • public class DecoratedJsonObject
extends java.lang.Object
    A DecoratedJsonObject wraps a JSONObject and decorates it with some methods.
